Azure Machine LEarning Studio


What is AI?

A computer that can imitate some aspect of human behavior
eg, number recognition, translation

train an ai based on past data, then train a model to create future prediction

machine learning
using unlabeled data and labeled data to train algorithm and model

Feature Data - raw data/unlabeled data
eg[x1,x2,x3]

label data - data that is labeled(1 is number, it is an orange, etc)
eg [y]

Algorithm -> Decision Tree -> SVM(Support vector machine) -> 

Once Model is trained
Data -> Model -> Label

Training data 
a. supervised learning(has labels)
    1. Regression(Numeric)
    2. Classification
        i. (Binary)(Is it this thing? is it not?)
        ii. multiclass(is it this genre?)
b. Unsupervised
    1 clustering(group)

ml.azure.com

the models can be run in a container/azure kubernetes


